- Hello, Kyle.

20:47.480 --> 20:49.013
- You wanted to see me?

20:49.148 --> 20:51.415
- Yeah, I did, um...

20:51.551 --> 20:56.754
- I'm sorry,
I know this is hard for you.

20:56.889 --> 20:59.023
- What?

20:59.158 --> 21:00.524
- Your son?

21:00.660 --> 21:04.895
- Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah,
no, yeah, uh, thank you.

21:05.031 --> 21:07.765
You know what the hardest part
about this life is, Kyle?

21:07.900 --> 21:12.970
- No sir, I don't.

21:13.106 --> 21:15.773
- The loneliness.

21:15.908 --> 21:18.075
- I'm sorry, sir.

21:18.211 --> 21:21.245
- You know what makes it
even more frustrating?

21:21.381 --> 21:23.214
- No sir, please tell me.

21:23.349 --> 21:28.552
- When you meet a woman,
she ignores you.

21:28.688 --> 21:32.223
I'm the -- President
of the United States.

21:32.358 --> 21:34.025
She's ignoring me.

21:36.729 --> 21:39.196
What do you think makes
them do that, Kyle?

21:39.332 --> 21:42.933
- Um, they may be afraid, sir.

21:43.069 --> 21:44.535
- Afraid of what?

21:44.671 --> 21:46.771
Look at me.

21:46.906 --> 21:49.240
- The power, sir.

21:49.375 --> 21:51.075
- I thought women liked power.

21:51.210 --> 21:53.144
- Not all women, sir.

21:53.279 --> 21:54.545
- So--so you're telling me

21:54.681 --> 21:59.617
