23:34.881 --> 23:36.347
- Yeah.

23:36.482 --> 23:39.049
- Tell him.

23:39.185 --> 23:42.419
- The agent that was shot
that night at Denise's place--

23:42.555 --> 23:44.989
- Max.
- What about him?

23:45.124 --> 23:46.791
- He was there.
- What?

23:46.926 --> 23:49.693
- The night that she left.

23:49.829 --> 23:52.830
I was in the back hiding,
and I saw him.

23:52.965 --> 23:56.000
And...she didn't seem like
she wanted to go,

23:56.135 --> 23:59.537
but he was putting on
white gloves to take her.

23:59.672 --> 24:03.874
