24:13.786 --> 24:15.386
- Okay.

24:15.521 --> 24:18.455
- What are we gonna do, Sam?

24:18.591 --> 24:21.025
- I don't know, I'm still trying
to wrap my head around it.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.493
- What?

24:22.628 --> 24:25.830
- Yeah, I'm still trying
to figure it all out.

24:25.965 --> 24:28.732
Make sure you don't say a word
to anyone about this, okay?

24:28.868 --> 24:30.801
- Okay.

24:30.937 --> 24:34.038
- What--what do you mean you--
you trying to figure it all out?

24:34.173 --> 24:36.907
- Barry, let me
talk to your dad.

24:37.043 --> 24:38.409
- Okay.

24:38.544 --> 24:40.311
- You know your way out?

24:40.446 --> 24:42.813
- As long as I don't see
that evil little bitch.

24:42.949 --> 24:45.916
- Hey, hey, look, I will--
