24:46.052 --> 24:47.685
- Alright.

24:50.156 --> 24:53.324
- Sam...what do you think?

24:53.459 --> 24:56.694
- This is bad, really bad.

24:56.829 --> 24:58.996
- Did he do something to her?

24:59.131 --> 25:00.264
- I can't say, Richard.

25:00.399 --> 25:03.334
- Damn!
