25:03.469 --> 25:05.936
- But I'm on it.

25:06.072 --> 25:07.571
- Okay.

25:09.475 --> 25:11.041
- Let me ask you something.

25:11.177 --> 25:12.509
- What?

25:12.645 --> 25:15.279
- Priscilla, is she
working with...

25:15.414 --> 25:16.914
- What?

25:17.049 --> 25:19.416
